(ns shimmers.view.about)

(defn index []
  [:div
   [:h1 "What is this?"]
   [:p "It's a collection of random computational generative sketches that I used to explore graphics programming and generative art."]
   [:p "Think of it as a digital sketchbook of various ideas I was exploring.
   Some of visualize algorithms or are graphical tests, while others explore
   generative constraints of a particular visual idea."]
   [:p "Some are interactive, some are static, some process video from a webcam."]
   [:p "My philosophy with this project was to publish whatever ideas I had as I
   explored them, as such none of these sketches are necessarily complete. I
   avoid self-curating as I found that stifled my ability to explore freely.
   Some of them I have revisited and tuned years later, and some never made it
   far enough to explore whatever concept I had."]])
